 management software?<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">For the fear of sounding like a broken record, we would have said that this is a piece of software which allows event planners to manage their events even better. The truth, however, is that this does not even begin to skim the surface of the matter.<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">In reality, an online event management software is an important tool which helps in all of the pre-event (registrations, payments processing, audience mapping, etc.), event (engagement, personalized service delivery, etc.) and post-event (follow-up, email outreach, etc.) stages of planning and organisation.\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">This shows how important it can be to the success of an event when used right. To put cream on the matter, they also make for better event planning with every event which has been run through them.<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">Now that we have that out of the way\u2026<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">What makes online event management software special?<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">Quite a lot, if you ask us. So that we don\u2019t launch into sentimental speeches of how much this piece of software has done for us, we will let the points do all the talking.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-34d1f14 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"34d1f14\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-a723c48\" data-id=\"a723c48\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eb3164f elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"eb3164f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/Professionalism.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1728\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/Professionalism.jpeg 700w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/Professionalism-300x200.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-538377c elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"538377c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">1) Professionalism\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dfa3e1a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dfa3e1a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv_text_element\"><div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv_text_element\"><div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv_text_element\"><p dir=\"ltr\">Every event management company has to put their best foot forward to convince the attendees to even come around. That is why we cringe when we see fliers, event advertisements, registration forms and such other important documents with third-party watermarks on them.\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">Besides taking the professionalism away from the event management company \u2013 and the brand they are representing \u2013 it also makes the event look cheap.<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">That will not happen with an online event management tool, allowing you to create customized templates that your clients and customers are used to. Way to stamp your identity on the market, if you ask us.<\/p><\/div><div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv-columns\"><div class=\"tcb-flex-row tcb-resized tcb--cols--2\"><div class=\"tcb-flex-col\" data-css=\"tve-u-16f6aec13d7\"><div class=\"tcb-col\"><div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv_text_element\">\u00a0<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4db63af elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"4db63af\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"109\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/Event-Marketing.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1732\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/Event-Marketing.jpeg 700w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/Event-Marketing-300x47.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e4ff66d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e4ff66d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">2) Marketing\n <\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-753c029 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"753c029\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv_text_element\"><p dir=\"ltr\">No matter how great your event is, you still have to market it.\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">Looking at many events across many years, it is obvious that marketing budget is one of the biggest costs of running the event itself. That, and we have not even mentioned the time that goes into such marketing.<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">What if we told you that you could cut back on the time and money, though?<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">Using these apps, you can sync with various social media channels and have a buzz created around your event. The best part is that all of these can be run on autopilot, giving you the time and resources to focus on more pressing parts of the event planning process.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c0fe7f7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"c0fe7f7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/Online-Event-Payments.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1729\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/Online-Event-Payments.jpeg 700w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/Online-Event-Payments-300x200.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a2336e6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a2336e6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">3) Handling Payments\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4c1f653 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4c1f653\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv_text_element\"><p dir=\"ltr\">How would you like to safely and securely collect payments, accept donations, keep track of all checks and credit card information without breaking a sweat? Because that\u2019s what you get when you use these online event management tools for your events.<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">Even if you were running a fundraiser \u2013 or accepting sponsorships for the event \u2013 this tool can help you dedicate a section to make that happen. The best part is that you don\u2019t even have to be on ground to approve, accept or process any of the payments since the system has been trained to do all that on your behalf.<\/p><\/div><div class=\"thrv_wrapper tve_image_caption\" data-css=\"tve-u-16f6aeae40a\">\u00a0<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3f79dc4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3f79dc4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"720\" height=\"398\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/ibm-connect-2015-registration-with-micepad.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1720\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/ibm-connect-2015-registration-with-micepad.jpeg 720w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/ibm-connect-2015-registration-with-micepad-300x166.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5220257 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5220257\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">4) Improving Registration\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eeb921e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"eeb921e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p dir=\"ltr\">Why wait by the phone to receive calls from potential attendees or scan through your email address to register interested applicants when you can have this automated too?<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">Day or night, online event management tools are equipped with the self-sufficiency to get the needed information from event attendees, work them into the system and assign them as needed. All you have to do is keep track of the attendees for personal purposes, and you are good to go.\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">You can even program the software to assign these attendees seats automatically, approve their feeding plan (if there is one) and handle their accommodation needs, if there be need for such.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c89cb2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"5c89cb2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/Follow-up-call-to-attendees.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1730\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/Follow-up-call-to-attendees.jpeg 700w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/4\/2021\/06\/Follow-up-call-to-attendees-300x200.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d31532d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d31532d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">5) Follow-Up\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e49da2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2e49da2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"tve_flt\" class=\"tve_flt tcb-style-wrap\"><div id=\"tve_editor\" class=\"tve_shortcode_editor\"><div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv_text_element\"><p dir=\"ltr\">Do you know how many event planners find it difficult to keep in touch with attendees after the event is over?\u00a0<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">For those who manage to do so, it would sometimes involve entering the contact details of each attendee into a new database. If they registered online, though, you are insured against going through all those forms of stress.<\/p><p dir=\"ltr\">You now have all the information you need in one place, and even get to ask the attendees if they would like to receive additional content from you after the event has ended. Seamless communication and consent, all in one breath.<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ssf fpss\"><div class=\"ssf-i\"><div class=\"ss\">\u00a0<\/div><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>So, you have also heard that some of the professionals in your industry have started using online event management software, and you [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1728,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[128],"tags":[114],"class_list":["post-1726","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-product-insights","tag-online-event-management-software"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1726","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1726"}],"version-history":[{"count":11,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1726\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3474,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1726\/revisions\/3474"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1728"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1726"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1726"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/hk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1726"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}